# [BESS](../wg/bess.html)

## Summary
The BESS (BGP Enabled Services) Working Group met at IETF 126. The session was chaired by Matthew Bocci and Jeffrey Zhang, with Mankamana Prasad Mishra serving as secretary. The meeting covered the status of various working group drafts, followed by presentations and technical discussions on EVPN optimized ingress replication, first-hop security, unknown MAC routes, per-flow designated forwarder (DF) election, multicast router state synchronization, auto-discovery (EAD) multipath, dual MPLS/SRv6 service advertisements, SRv6 deployment migration, experimental route types, and interconnecting domains with IBGP.

